<div class="faq-wrapper">
  <h2 class="faq-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <button class="faq-question">Are your products real or artificial?</button>
    <div class="faq-answer">
      <p>All of our products at GS Foliage are <strong>100% real and naturally sourced</strong> — never artificial. Carefully preserved, many can last <strong>for years</strong> with proper care.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <button class="faq-question">What kinds of decorative items do you carry?</button>
    <div class="faq-answer">
      <p>We offer pine cones, birch poles, dried florals, and custom-finished decor — all natural and preserved, with options for painted or glittered finishes.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
  <button class="faq-question">Can I see examples of how your products look when used in real settings?</button>
  <div class="faq-answer">
    <p>Yes! We regularly share real-life styling examples from our clients and in-house shoots. You can find them on our gallery or Instagram, or by request.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="faq-item">
  <button class="faq-question">Do you offer seasonal or themed collections?</button>
  <div class="faq-answer">
    <p>Yes — we release themed and seasonal collections year-round. We can also customize pieces to match any season or color scheme.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="faq-item">
  <button class="faq-question">What customization options do you offer?</button>
  <div class="faq-answer">
    <p>We offer painted finishes, glitter accents, branded packaging, and custom assortments — all tailored to your needs.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="faq-item">
  <button class="faq-question">Can I order small quantities to test your products?</button>
  <div class="faq-answer">
    <p>Yes, we offer trial orders so you can test quality before placing a larger one.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="faq-item">
  <button class="faq-question">Where are you located and do you ship nationwide?</button>
  <div class="faq-answer">
    <p>We’re based in Manalapan, NJ, and we ship nationwide for all business sizes.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="faq-item">
  <button class="faq-question">What makes your products different from others I’ve seen online?</button>
  <div class="faq-answer">
    <p>Our products are 100% natural, preserved, customizable, and beautifully presented. We import in bulk to maintain variety and stock year-round.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="faq-item">
  <button class="faq-question">How long have you been in business?</button>
  <div class="faq-answer">
    <p>We’ve been family-owned and operated for over 30 years — trusted for our service, quality, and reliability.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="faq-item">
  <button class="faq-question">Do you sell wholesale or to businesses like mine?</button>
  <div class="faq-answer">
    <p>Yes! We work with businesses of all sizes — no minimums required, and tailored pricing available.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="faq-item">
  <button class="faq-question">Can I customize the color or finish of the items I order?</button>
  <div class="faq-answer">
    <p>Yes — we offer hand-painted and glitter finishes for most of our natural products. You choose the color, and we’ll make it happen.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="faq-item">
  <button class="faq-question">What’s the turnaround time for custom orders?</button>
  <div class="faq-answer">
    <p>Most custom orders ship within 7–14 business days. For large or time-sensitive orders, just contact us directly.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="faq-item">
  <button class="faq-question">Do you offer custom packaging with our branding?</button>
  <div class="faq-answer">
    <p>Yes! We can provide branded boxes, labels, and packaging to align with your retail or event needs.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="faq-item">
  <button class="faq-question">What are your minimum order quantities for businesses?</button>
  <div class="faq-answer">
    <p>There’s no minimum — order what you need, when you need it. Wholesale pricing available for larger volumes.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="faq-item">
  <button class="faq-question">How do I place a wholesale or repeat order?</button>
  <div class="faq-answer">
    <p>You can contact us directly via email or phone, or use our website form. Reorders are easy — we keep records of past orders.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="faq-item">
  <button class="faq-question">Can I speak to someone directly before placing a large order?</button>
  <div class="faq-answer">
    <p>Of course. We’re happy to talk through product options, lead times, and packaging personally.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="faq-item">
  <button class="faq-question">How do you ensure product quality, especially with natural items?</button>
  <div class="faq-answer">
    <p>We hand-inspect and carefully package each order. Our preservation process ensures durability and beauty.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="faq-item">
  <button class="faq-question">What happens if something arrives damaged or isn’t what I expected?</button>
  <div class="faq-answer">
    <p>We’ll make it right — fast. Just reach out and we’ll send a replacement or refund without delay.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="faq-item">
  <button class="faq-question">Do you offer discounts for bulk or recurring orders?</button>
  <div class="faq-answer">
    <p>Yes — we offer tiered discounts for high-volume or repeat clients. Reach out for a custom quote.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="faq-item">
  <button class="faq-question">Can I see a catalog or pricing sheet for your full product line?</button>
  <div class="faq-answer">
    <p>Yes! You can download our latest catalog here: <a href="#" target="_blank">Download Catalog</a>. Or contact us for a tailored list.</p>
  </div>
</div>
<!-- Repeat this block below for each FAQ -->
  <!-- I'll send the full version with all 20 Q&As in the next message -->
</div>

<style>
  .faq-wrapper {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 60px 20px;
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
  }

  .faq-title {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    color: #2c2c2c;
  }

  .faq-item {
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    padding: 20px 0;
  }

  .faq-question {
    background: none;
    border: none;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-align: left;
    width: 100%;
    cursor: pointer;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .faq-answer {
    display: none;
    margin-top: 15px;
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .faq-question::after {
    content: '+';
    float: right;
    font-size: 20px;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .faq-question.active::after {
    content: '-';
  }
</style>

<script>
  document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function () {
    document.querySelectorAll('.faq-question').forEach(btn => {
      btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
        btn.classList.toggle('active');
        const answer = btn.nextElementSibling;
        answer.style.display = answer.style.display === 'block' ? 'none' : 'block';
      });
    });
  });
</script>

